snippet.title: BioGun - Official Closed Beta Trailer
snippet.description:
Get another look at the world of BioGun, including some of the threats you'll face, in this latest trailer for the upcoming Metroidvania game set inside your dog. Fight for your animal companion and for dogkind in BioGun's closed beta.

#Gaming #GameTrailers #BioGun
